analysis.reasoning: Overall B produces a stronger result list for the broad query 'Fietsen'. It shows a better mix of bikes and useful bike-related accessories (locks, bags, panniers) alongside bicycles and helmets, giving broader coverage and more shopper value. The top items in B are more diverse and useful to different shopper intents (buying a bike vs. buying bike accessories). A has more helmet-heavy placements and near-duplicate bike imagery among the top results, reducing variety and likely hurting the experience for users seeking a range of bicycle options.
